 "remarks": "Beautifully updated 2bedroom, 1.5bath unit located in the rear of the complex offering privacy and easy access to visitor parking. This home features an updated kitchen and baths, hardwood floors throughout, and a large living room. Enjoy a new slider door leading to a private deck ideal for entertaining. Both bedrooms offer California Closets and comfortable space. Brand new improvements include refrigerator, appliances, washing machine, hot water heater, front door, and three window A/C units. Crown molding adds a refined touch, and the layout provides excellent storage. Prime location-walking distance to Newfield Shopping Center, minutes to Metro North, downtown Stamford, restaurants, shopping, and major commuter routes. Low HOA makes this a standout value in a highly convenient area. Welcome Home!",
